 2. Factory Design Pattern (Advanced Polymorphism)
 Question

Design a Driver Factory using polymorphism.

Answer
interface DriverFactory {
    WebDriver createDriver();
}

class ChromeFactory implements DriverFactory {
    public WebDriver createDriver() {
        return new ChromeDriver();
    }
}

class FirefoxFactory implements DriverFactory {
    public WebDriver createDriver() {
        return new FirefoxDriver();
    }
}

Usage:

DriverFactory factory = new ChromeFactory();
WebDriver driver = factory.createDriver();
 Expectation
Interface-based design
Loose coupling

