10. Real Framework Scenario (Retry Logic)
Question

Override method to add retry logic.

 Answer
class BaseAction {
    void click() {
        System.out.println("Click once");
    }
}

class RetryAction extends BaseAction {
    @Override
    void click() {
        for(int i=0; i<3; i++) {
            try {
                System.out.println("Trying click " + i);
                break;
            } catch(Exception e) {}
        }
    }
}
